## Solana Settlement (Optional)

GitExchange now supports Solana RPC transaction verification for BUY execution:

- Submit a normal BUY issue title (`BUY <ticker> <qty>`)
- Add `wallet:` and `signature:` lines in the issue body
- AgentR verifies a confirmed transfer to the configured treasury wallet before settlement

Configuration lives in `data/config.json` under the `solana` section (`rpc_url`, `treasury_wallet`, `usd_per_sol`, and policy flags).

---

## AgentR Automation

AgentR orchestration and self-healing are built in:

- `engine/agentr_orchestrator.py` runs price updates, market events, rendering, and health checks with retry
- `engine/self_heal.py` repairs common state drift and validates integrity
- `.github/workflows/agentr-orchestrator.yml` runs end-to-end automation
- `.github/workflows/self-healing-ci.yml` runs compile + strict self-heal checks in CI

